Product Details*

This dock works with every Dell E Series Laptop. It also works with every Precision model laptop made since 2010. It does not work with Vostro, Inspiron or XPS family laptops.

You can leave your monitor and all your peripherals and your AC adapter connected to this docking station. Just attach your laptop and in one single second you have access to your printer, keyboard, mouse, external hard drives and more. Turn your laptop into a desktop computer in a flash.

Maximize your workspace with this Dell E-Port Replicator. This Dell E-Port Replicator gives you a comfortable work space where you can plug a keyboard, mouse and monitor to the port replicator and use your laptop like a desktop! Simplified connectivity facilitates a single interface to connect to your printer, monitor or other peripheral devices. Features 2 USB 3.0 ports!

Here's a little know fact about the PR03X. It supports 4 displays. You can plug 3 into the port replicator (1 15 pin analog, 1 DVI and one display port) and leave your laptop LCD open as a third display.

The last consideration is the AC adapter (if any) that you want. You can use the one that came with your laptop. If you only take your laptop with you occasionally that is the best bet, nothing else to buy. If you are on the road with your laptop frequently buying an AC adapter is worthwhile. The easiest way to pick the right AC adapter is to look at the onethat came with your laptop. Generally, the bigger the laptop display, the more powerful AC adater you will want.
